<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِنَّ فِي النَّاسِ شَيَاطِنَ ... وَأَشْبَاهَ الْأَبَالِسْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>جَعَلَ اللَّهُ لِحَاهُمْ ... لِلْمَطَامِيعِ مَكَانِسْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَنَا فِي بَيْتِي خَوْفًا مِنْ ... فَسَادِ النَّاسِ جَالِسْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَتَرَانِي ذَا اعْتِصَامٍ ... وَمِنَ الْأُمَّةِ آيِسْ»<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>